2. **Reusability**: Components can be used across different screens
3. **Testability**: Individual components can be tested in isolation 
4. **Type Safety**: Sealed classes and data classes prevent runtime errors
5. **Consistency**: All similar UI elements look and behave the same
6. **Scalability**: Easy to add new settings without code duplication

